{"about_the_game":"<strong>Forests, Fields and Fortresses</strong> is a mix of a puzzle and a board game in which you have to build your kingdom. Try on the role of a ruler, piece together your lands and ensure the prosperity of your people. Two game modes will be available to you, each with its own unique gameplay:<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113450/extras/Title_PuzzleMode.png?t=1680682574\" /><br><strong>Puzzle Mode</strong>. Manually created levels with a small number of pieces of territory. Your goal is to place them in such a way as to earn the required amount of Gold.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113450/extras/Title_AdventureMode.png?t=1680682574\" /><br><strong>Adventure Mode</strong>. Start the game with a randomly created field and an endless supply of pieces of territory. Earn enough Gold before the playing field is full to successfully complete the game season and move on to the next one. Unlock new Spells, Game Events and Starting Locality Types to diversify your playthroughs.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113450/extras/FFF_Gif_2.gif?t=1680682574\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Sacred Grove","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2113450/94ca274e6f43d31151025db42db34ffc54ec0c25.jpg"},{"name":"Village","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2113450/75becc58501d991e6291a6307b58463fb39aa95d.jpg"},{"name":"Fortress","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2113450/1ac4c5541bc0cab303f26de75d6f4355ae25fd91.jpg"},{"name":"Fishing Boats","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2113450/0c4c07f6309305768e78c0f25346d6074b313ee7.jpg"},{"name":"Ancient Obelisk","path":"https://cdn.akamai.s